name: ATH9KInjector
description: A Lilu plugin for patching AirPortAtheros40.kext hence enabling Atheros AR9K based cards in macOS.
changes:
#### v1.2.6
- Added Lilu 1.2.6 compatibility
- Added macOS Mojave support (untested)
- Updated injector kext to be in sync with plugin version.
guide:
#### Features
